{"tid":2514583,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭秀文新歌呼應《我們都是這樣長大的》　透視貼身裙印歌名顯心思","createTime":"2021-05-03T10:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:47:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27aa8086db65b9472e2d7e357803b23058074e51","tid":2514583,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"鄭秀文（Sammi）繼上年的《如何忍眼淚》後，今日（3/5）亦推出新歌《萬物有時》，並率先安排在電台首播，樂迷要再等一段時間，才可以於各大音樂平台收聽。<br />\n<br />\nSammi在Instagram中透露，新歌歌詞與兩年前名作《我們都是這樣長大的》呼應，她解釋：「我們每個人都在各自的經歷中成長，掙扎，進步，希望或失落，變化。甚至面對生與死。我們都是這樣長大的。最終我們也會慢慢發現，很多事情不能急於一時，很多事情我們找不到答案，但始終：萬物有時。就像這首歌的最後一句：人在經歷中，得失總有意思。」在照片中的造型都經過度身訂造，不論指甲或是透視連身裙，都印上「萬物有時」，與歌名互相呼應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210503/465929220632088576045321.jpeg/UvRFJ3qc-Ep3TOSrHSphiMJYzZ8ERfifGRkQbRkZEG0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210503%2F465929220632088576045321.jpeg%2FUvRFJ3qc-Ep3TOSrHSphiMJYzZ8ERfifGRkQbRkZEG0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=69fc654a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210503/465929417458192384896041.jpeg/t5vZjXBl84Uww0gV9HZxfDgfmuCgpiiKQ2W8YUNlvGE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210503%2F465929417458192384896041.jpeg%2Ft5vZjXBl84Uww0gV9HZxfDgfmuCgpiiKQ2W8YUNlvGE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c8ada063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62d2425d11023b6e8372b8e98efc6412950d7552","tid":2514583,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"她的胸部不是這樣長大的"},{"pid":"7b565da9a890861374f604ab1a1b2d1ad023c54e","tid":2514583,"uid":35296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"個妝正常返咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86745